{"id":1457,"date":"2024-11-13T10:54:21","date_gmt":"2024-11-13T03:54:21","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/conicboulevard.vn\/?p=1457"},"modified":"2025-04-21T23:32:47","modified_gmt":"2025-04-21T16:32:47","slug":"hon-500-trieu-usd-fdi-do-vao-binh-duong-chi-trong-2-thang-dau-nam-2025","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/hon-500-trieu-usd-fdi-do-vao-binh-duong-chi-trong-2-thang-dau-nam-2025\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u01a1n 500 tri\u1ec7u USD FDI \u0111\u1ed5 v\u00e0o B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 trong 2 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2025"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i>Trong hai th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2025, t\u1ec9nh B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 515,3 tri\u1ec7u USD v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i (FDI) v\u00e0 h\u01a1n 7.600 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd kinh doanh trong n\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a t\u1ec9nh trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kinh t\u1ebf to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/i><\/p>\n<h2><b>B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00fat v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 FDI \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2025<\/b><\/h2>\n<p>Theo b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u1eeb UBND t\u1ec9nh B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, trong hai th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2025, t\u1ec9nh \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 515,3 tri\u1ec7u USD v\u1ed1n FDI v\u00e0 7.613 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd kinh doanh trong n\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn nay, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4.433 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng v\u1ed1n 42,5 t\u1ef7 USD v\u00e0 74.949 doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng v\u1ed1n 820.000 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1554\" src=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/binh-duong-cong-nghiep-2-16672941796292000815035-250-0-1500-2000-crop-1709036017718953225806-1536x960-1.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1536\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/binh-duong-cong-nghiep-2-16672941796292000815035-250-0-1500-2000-crop-1709036017718953225806-1536x960-1.webp 1536w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/binh-duong-cong-nghiep-2-16672941796292000815035-250-0-1500-2000-crop-1709036017718953225806-1536x960-1-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/binh-duong-cong-nghiep-2-16672941796292000815035-250-0-1500-2000-crop-1709036017718953225806-1536x960-1-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/binh-duong-cong-nghiep-2-16672941796292000815035-250-0-1500-2000-crop-1709036017718953225806-1536x960-1-768x480.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p th\u00e1ng 2\/2025 \u01b0\u1edbc t\u0103ng 20,6% so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3; l\u0169y k\u1ebf 2 th\u00e1ng, \u01b0\u1edbc t\u0103ng 6,7% so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3. T\u1ed5ng m\u1ee9c b\u00e1n l\u1ebb h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a v\u00e0 doanh thu d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng \u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1t 31.995 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, t\u0103ng 21,4% so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3; l\u0169y k\u1ebf 2 th\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1ea1t 63.890 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, t\u0103ng 14,5% so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3.\u00a0<\/p>\n<h2><b>T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a v\u1ed1n FDI \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/b><\/h2>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng thu h\u00fat m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1ed1n FDI \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Theo c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia B\u0110S, s\u1ef1 gia t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y nhu c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u1edf cho chuy\u00ean gia v\u00e0 lao \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra nhu c\u1ea7u l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c khu c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p, v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 li\u00ean quan.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb B\u0110S v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat th\u00eam c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1556\" src=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/trien-lam-det-may-1709115901520421041991-1536x864-1.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/trien-lam-det-may-1709115901520421041991-1536x864-1.webp 1536w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/trien-lam-det-may-1709115901520421041991-1536x864-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/trien-lam-det-may-1709115901520421041991-1536x864-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/trien-lam-det-may-1709115901520421041991-1536x864-1-768x432.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng giao th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec7n \u00edch c\u00f4ng c\u1ed9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u01b0 d\u00e2n v\u00e0 doanh nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng cao gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb B\u0110S trong khu v\u1ef1c.<\/p>\n<h2><b>Tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng trong n\u0103m 2025<\/b><\/h2>\n<p>Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c ph\u00eda Nam, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n trong n\u0103m 2025. C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia B\u0110S c\u0169ng d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n lu\u1eadt s\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed5i, b\u1ed5 sung (Lu\u1eadt \u0110\u1ea5t \u0111ai, Lu\u1eadt Nh\u00e0 \u1edf, Lu\u1eadt Kinh doanh B\u0110S, Lu\u1eadt \u0110\u1ea7u t\u01b0, Lu\u1eadt Quy ho\u1ea1ch\u2026) ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1555\" src=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Binh-Duong-thuc-day-dau-tu-voi-chinh-sach-mien-tien-thue-dat.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"630\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Binh-Duong-thuc-day-dau-tu-voi-chinh-sach-mien-tien-thue-dat.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Binh-Duong-thuc-day-dau-tu-voi-chinh-sach-mien-tien-thue-dat-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Binh-Duong-thuc-day-dau-tu-voi-chinh-sach-mien-tien-thue-dat-1024x538.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Binh-Duong-thuc-day-dau-tu-voi-chinh-sach-mien-tien-thue-dat-768x403.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, trong qu\u00fd I\/2025, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac n\u00e0y tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng khi l\u1ee3i su\u1ea5t cho thu\u00ea B\u0110S B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng thu\u1ed9c top \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft l\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng thu h\u00fat h\u01a1n 500 tri\u1ec7u USD v\u1ed1n FDI trong hai th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2025 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho s\u1ee9c h\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a t\u1ec9nh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c n\u00e0y, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn cho c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong hai th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2025, t\u1ec9nh B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 515,3 tri\u1ec7u USD v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i (FDI) v\u00e0 h\u01a1n 7.600 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd kinh doanh trong n\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a t\u1ec9nh trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kinh [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":1554,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"rank_math_lock_modified_date":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1457","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts